  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Historic Interest Rate</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loio91518dfed49043c7885bb064e7b4040c\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Historic Interest Rate</h1><div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\"></p>\n<div class=\"p\">With this card, you can choose to see the daily or monthly reference interest rate trend in the\npast. You can switch between the following two views:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loio91518dfed49043c7885bb064e7b4040c__ul_lrr_zc3_ddb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Daily</span></p><p class=\"p\">Historic reference interest rates in the last 7 days are displayed.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Monthly</span></p><p class=\"p\">Historic reference interest rates in the last 12 months are displayed.</p></li>\n</ul></div>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" href=\"9a6016237596418bba8312f9e9d8ce5a.html\">Interest Rate Overview</a>.</p>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
